  "text": "This study is associated with some limitations. First, no detailed questionnaire was used regarding the subject's history of injury to identify the environment in which the injury occurred. Among skaters, off-ice training is one of the most common precipitating risk factors for injury, [CITATION_1] and we were unable to precisely evaluate the mechanisms underlying such injuries.",
